bsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;\r\n &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;\r\n &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '       收藏 | 转给毕业生！找工作前，这10个名词你一定要知道', '收藏 | 转给毕业生！找工作前，这10个名词你一定要知道', '/Uploads/Picture/uploads/20161123/58350d0dad40f.png', '0', '2016-10-29', null, '', '0', null, '靠谱APP，可以边找工作边赚钱~找工作的小伙伴可以试试看', '35', '', '1', '0', '1', null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `uha_classnews` VALUES ('39', '&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 17px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;➤&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;1.你说话有逻辑吗？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;对一个leader而言有两件事非常重要，把事想清楚，把话说清楚。如果常常事与愿违，可能是你没把话说清楚。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;而作为一个下属，执行完工作需要汇报工作，leader又常常打断你的汇报“说重点，用一句话告诉我。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;不思考的工作是一种舒服的状态，因为它符合人性，我们都喜欢处于这种状态，习惯把各种各样的小事叠加在一起，在信息尚未完全在大脑加工就开始跟leader汇报，可是最后的结果却都不尽如意。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;“boss，A总今天没空，B总出差了，周三回来，C总明天之后都可以，另外，周三订不到会议室，会议安排在周四上午10点可以吗？”这个员工应该很漂亮吧。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;也许你看到这样的案例笑了，但反思一下你平常的工作，是不是也经常话到嘴边就说出来了？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;你和把话说清楚中间，只差一个金字塔原理的方法论，并不断有意识的训练。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;我们可以把以上对话经过金字塔原理的加工，“boss，今天的会议我们想改再周四上午10点，你看可以吗？因为A、B、C总那个时间比较方便，会议室也只有那一天有空。A总……B总……C总……。会议室……”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;为了别让你的leader在听的过程中处于焦灼的状态“那TM到底什么时候？”， 先告诉他结论，如果他想继续了解情况可以再按与会人员和会议室情况分别汇报，逻辑清晰的你可能会让人觉得更靠谱。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;➤&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;2.记住这4个原则，把握金字塔原理&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;http://rlzy.unohacha.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161121/1479733866284771.png\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1479733866284771.png\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;QQ截图20161121210724.png\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;结论先行&lt;/strong&gt;，&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;每次开口前先想想，如果大家只能记住你所说的一句话你希望是哪一句，先把它说出来。&lt;/strong&gt;每次给出过多杂乱的信息，会使听者难以理解你要表达的意思，反而他会在大脑不断组合，因为人总是会按照自己已有的认知去理解，导致他理解的未必是你想表达的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;比如：美国有一个节目是主持人采访一些小朋友，主持人问一个小朋友你的梦想是什么？小朋友说飞行员，主持人接着问“那如果你正在驾驶的飞机没有汽油了你会怎么办？”，小朋友说“我会让乘客都绑好安全带不要动，然后我用降落伞跳下去”，大家哄堂大笑打断了小朋友的说话，大家普遍会以自己的想法认为“这就是人性的恶，自私”，但是故事的结论是小孩希望跳下去之后去寻找汽油回来救这些乘客。所以，人们总是会带有主观意识去理解，直接先说结论，再去阐述，否则等别人有了自己的理解后，解释成本更大。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;以上统下，选择自上而下的表达。&lt;/strong&gt;我们已经把结论放在最上面了，接下来需要阐述这个结论，一层一层的往下剖析，上一层的思想应该是对下一层思想的总结。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;归类分组&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;，把同类的问题归在一组。&lt;/strong&gt;人的大脑会自动的将所有的事务以某种秩序组织起来，比如看到手机、充电器、手表三个词语，你一定会把手机和充电器联系在一起，所以有秩序的表达可以使听者更容易记忆；乔治·A·米勒提出奇妙的数字“7±2”，大脑的短期记忆无法一次性容纳7个以上的记忆项目，记忆力好的可能可以记住9个，有的可能只能记住5个，3个比较容易记住。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;逻辑递进，每一组的思想必须按照逻辑顺序排列，单单归类分组是不够的，需要把它提高一个思想层次，否则归类分组也是徒劳。&lt;/strong&gt;比如：苹果、梨子、香蕉、胡萝卜、西红柿、菠菜。单纯的归类分组应该是把它分成两组，但是依旧需要记忆6项。当我们把苹果、梨子、香蕉归类分组并逻辑递进为水果，而胡萝卜、西红柿、菠菜为蔬菜，这样我们就只需要记忆2项了。如果妈妈让我们去买这6样东西，我们只需要记得买水果和蔬菜，再想水果和蔬菜各有哪些，这样记忆应该就容易多了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;➤&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;3.金字塔的内部结构&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;http://rlzy.unohacha.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161121/1479733894770168.png\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1479733894770168.png\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;QQ截图20161121211122.png\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;white-space: normal;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;纵向方向，本质上读者阅读文章是为了获取自己所需要的信息，我们可以通过不断的发出新的信息并引起读者的疑问，然后在下一个层次进行回答，直到读者接受你说的思想而不再提出疑问为止。通过这样的方式也能够极大的引起读者的兴趣。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;white-space: normal;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;横向方向，也就是在每一个层次内回答问题的时候，要么使用演绎推理，要么使用归纳推理。演绎推理是通过大前提、小前提、结论的方式，例如：①大前提：所有看了本篇文章的人都会好好说话，②小前提：你看了本篇文章，③结论：所以你会好好说话；而归纳推理是：西红柿鸡蛋盖浇饭十分美味，西红柿鸡蛋盖浇饭十分快速，西红柿鸡蛋盖浇饭十分廉价，所以中午推荐西红柿鸡蛋盖浇饭。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;我们需要注意在归纳推理的时候要遵循MECE原则（mutually exclusive，collectively exhaustive），各部分之间相互独立，所有部分完全穷尽。相互独立即不能出现两者概念相同的情况，完全穷尽就是要把所有可能的情况罗列出来。使用这样的原则可以让你把事情想得更加透彻。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;http://rlzy.unohacha.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161121/1479733920748968.png\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1479733920748968.png\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;QQ截图20161121211147.png\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;金字塔的顶端，如果我们直接向读者发出结论，冲击力过强不容易让读者接受，反而会茫然失措。为了避免这种情况，我们可以采用写序言讲故事的形式来给读者介绍一下大概的背景和冲突，这些应该都是读者已知的信息，更容易引起读者共鸣，从冲突开始读者可能就会提出疑问，这时我们就可以回到纵向方向开始回答作者的疑问。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 17px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;➤&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;4.搭建属于你的金字塔&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;http://rlzy.unohacha.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161121/1479733949216082.png\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1479733949216082.png\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;QQ截图20161121211217.png\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;white-space: normal;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;如果你已经想清楚了要讨论的内容，自上而下法搭建金字塔结构一般要比较容易。我们先确定好文章的主题，并根据对读者的了解设想该主题会有哪些疑问，然后就可以按照我们之前说的“背景-冲突-问题-回答”的方式写序言了，紧接着与受众进行疑问/回答式的对话，最后对受众的新疑问重复进行疑问/回答式对话。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;white-space: normal;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;http://rlzy.unohacha.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161121/1479734456724845.png\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1479734456724845.png\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;QQ截图20161121212041.png\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;当然更多时候，我们并不能在一开始的时候就想清楚金字塔的顶部，不能确定主题思想，不知道读者知道什么不知道什么，我们无法采取自上而下的方法。此时，我们可以采用自下而上法，退到下一层次罗列出所有的思想要点，找出这些思想要点之间的关系，最后得出结论，并且倒推出序言。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 17px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;➤&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;5.练习，总结出自己表达的方法论&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;http://rlzy.unohacha.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161121/1479733983804946.png\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1479733983804946.png\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;QQ截图20161121211247.png\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;学会科学的表达，会让你的学习/工作/生活都事半功倍，金字塔的适用范围很广，但它也并非万能，应该在合理的情境中使用，比如老板要fire一个员工，应该不会一上来就告诉他：你被解雇了，原因如下……！再或者医生要告知病人病情时……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(73, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;表达是一门艺术，它可以是口头也可以是书面，牢记上面的一些小方法，并且不断的有意识训练自己，一定会有很大的改善，不信你试试看？在练习的过程中还可以总结出一套自己表达的方法论。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', ' 对一个leader而言有两件事非常重要，把事想清楚，把话说清楚。', '如何快速让你表达变得更有逻辑', '/Uploads/Picture/uploads/20161121/583303294a4b0.jpg', '0', '2016-11-21', null, null, '0', null, null, '2', '', '1', '0', '1', null, null, '');
INSERT INTO `uha_classnews` VALUES ('46', '&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;最近，朋友圈中的招人帖、英雄帖逐渐多了起来，又到了一年中应届生和企业招聘部门最惶恐、最忙碌的时节。应届生们，你们终于可以大显身手了。为什么这么说？因为，企业是喜欢新人的。诚然，要将职场小鲜肉培养成职场白骨精，需要大量的时间、金钱、精力，甚至一定程度上还要冒着“投资失败”的风险。特别是随着应届生们已经熟练掌握各种面试技巧后，这种风险的比例又大大提升了。即便如此，只要是渴望发展的企业，他们依然会张开双臂，欢迎你们。因为，你们充满活力和激情，敢于创新和突破，在还没有被任何条条框框束缚前，是一张具有“犊牛”性质的白纸。在这个创新的时代，这是再好不过的事情了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;大家可能要问，为什么企业需要新人，可年年还是最难就业季呢？造成这个问题的原因有很多；主要是用人单位和就业人员之间的关注点不同。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;事实上，从企业的角度看，每个最难就业季的背后都有一个最难招聘季。每年，虽然毕业生看上去很多，但是真正能符合企业基本要求的，却少之又少。说到底，企业不是学校，没有时间会耐心地等待你慢慢成长。相反，企业要生存和发展，需要创造财富和社会价值，因此，他们需要的是可以为企业带来价值的人；至少是通过培养后，能为企业创造价值的人，而绝不是只会做命题作文的好学生。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;可以说，企业的期待和要求和应届生们的整体素质存在着巨大的供需不平衡。正因为这种鸿沟，所以有必要来谈谈企业是如何来看待人才的，他们究竟需要什么样的人才？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161202/1480659685834424.jpg\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1480659685834424.jpg\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;640.webp (1).jpg\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;虽然每个企业都有各自的招聘标准和人才体系，但归总来看，离不开三类指标SKA：Skill技能、Knowledge知识、Attitude态度（价值观）。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\\&quot;&gt;如果用学校的考核指标来说，SK相当于你拥有取得优异成绩的知识和能力，而A则代表了你有取得优异成绩的意愿以及你是否愿意以学校要求的方式参加竞争。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-tools=\\&quot;135编辑器\\&quot; data-id=\\&quot;87845\\&quot; data-color=\\&quot;rgb(94, 145, 189)\\&quot; data-custom=\\&quot;rgb(94, 145, 189)\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-width=\\&quot;20em\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 20em; text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 6px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(94, 145, 189); transform: rotate(360deg);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px dashed white;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-brushtype=\\&quot;text\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;先来说知识和技能&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section data-width=\\&quot;20em\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: -1.8em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 20em; height: 3em; background-image: url(&amp;quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/z9433rAGTDd362svibwfNT35N8r9hs3elMShehLtO1rTRxAafDjjbwP30HSN7Ps1JguC6GkIgDl7icL3nbeOcFRQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;quot;); background-size: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;知识和技能可以被看作是硬性指标，通常被列在招聘启事和职位说明中。它分为通用领域和专业领域。比如：office操作软件、团队合作能力、沟通能力、学习能力等岗位中都需要知识技能都属于通用领域。财务岗位的会计上岗资格，IT岗位需要的的IT技术，医师的医师资格等专业性强的则属于专业领域。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;根据1996年OECD对知识经济的阐释，它将知识为四种类型：knowledge-what(事实知识)、knowledge-why(原理知识)、knowledge-how(技能知识)、knowledge-who(人际知识)。这四类知识囊括了企业对于人才的所有硬性指标。当前，在学校大量教授的是事实知识和原理知识。如何将事实和原理知识应用到工作中去，转化为技能知识，并能与同事、客户、供应商、政府等部门进行良好的互动（人际知识），这是应届生们所需要跨越的一大门槛，也是企业培养和发展人才的重要环节。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-tools=\\&quot;135编辑器\\&quot; data-id=\\&quot;87845\\&quot; data-color=\\&quot;rgb(94, 145, 189)\\&quot; data-custom=\\&quot;rgb(94, 145, 189)\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-width=\\&quot;20em\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 20em; text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 6px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(94, 145, 189); transform: rotate(360deg);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px dashed white;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-brushtype=\\&quot;text\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;再来说价值观&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section data-width=\\&quot;20em\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: -1.8em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 20em; height: 3em; background-image: url(&amp;quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/z9433rAGTDd362svibwfNT35N8r9hs3elMShehLtO1rTRxAafDjjbwP30HSN7Ps1JguC6GkIgDl7icL3nbeOcFRQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;quot;); background-size: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;如果说知识技能是看得见、摸得着的指标；那价值观就是看不见、摸不着的指标。价值观究竟是什么？&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.5px;\\&quot;&gt;“它是人认定事物、辩定是非的一种思维或价值取向”。它是个人做事的基准，是内心的一把尺，帮助你鉴别是非对错，告诉你应该如何取舍。但是，每个人的这把尺，在不同的事件上，尺度是千差万别的。例如，虔诚的基督徒们就坚持离婚是罪恶的。他们在“离婚”这件事上的尺度就和别人不同，这是基督徒们的价值观。又如，日常生活中，有些人是坚定的守时主义者，而另一些人则认为差个5、6分钟也不是什么大事。这是人在“守时”上的尺度差异。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;类似的，企业也有自己的价值观。对于员工来说，要按照企业的需要调整自己的价值观，并以企业要求的方式完成工作任务，这点就显得尤为重要。在优秀的企业中，从员工的身上能够反映企业的价值观。人们可以从这些员工的一言一行感到一种气质和精神。因此在甄选人才时，企业的确会考虑候选人的人品、气质、行为等软性指标，是否符合企业的价值观。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;价值观相符在招聘中究竟有多重要？很多人可能听过一些资深HR或者行业大牛在谈论招聘经验时提到，只要3-5秒就可以判断一个候选人是否是自己想要的人。这听起来很玄乎，甚至有失公允；却恰恰反映了价值观在甄选人才中的重要性和直观性。就像谈恋爱时，要看“眼缘”和“feel”一样；其实，企业在招聘时，会非常关注个人的想法能否和企业的要求保持一致；而且在相同条件下，往往偏爱那些价值观更靠近企业的人。这是因为知识和技能是能够培养和突击的，而要改变一个人的价值观是极其困难，甚至是不可能的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-tools=\\&quot;135编辑器\\&quot; data-id=\\&quot;2\\&quot; data-color=\\&quot;rgb(94, 145, 189)\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-bcless=\\&quot;darken\\&quot; placeholder=\\&quot;深色边框标题\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 10px 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 2px 2px 4px; border-left: 10px solid rgb(53, 93, 128); border-top-color: rgb(53, 93, 128); border-right-color: rgb(53, 93, 128); border-bottom-color: rgb(53, 93, 128); background-color: rgb(94, 145, 189);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-tools=\\&quot;135编辑器\\&quot; data-id=\\&quot;86276\\&quot; data-color=\\&quot;rgb(223, 236, 248)\\&quot; data-custom=\\&quot;rgb(223, 236, 248)\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-width=\\&quot;100%\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 1em; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(223, 236, 248); display: inline-block; width: 640px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 111, 177); background-color: rgb(223, 236, 248);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 1.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-top: 1px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); border-right-color: rgb(223, 236, 248); border-bottom-color: rgb(223, 236, 248); border-left-color: rgb(223, 236, 248);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-brushtype=\\&quot;text\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(23, 54, 93);\\&quot;&gt;既然价值观如此重要，作为职场新人，应该如何去了解一家企业的价值取向呢？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; border-top: 0.8em solid rgb(223, 236, 248); border-bottom-color: rgb(223, 236, 248); height: 10px; border-left: 0.8em solid transparent !important; border-right: 0.8em solid transparent !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;最快捷的方式，是通过宣传途径，找到企业对价值观定义。这些价值主张，表明了企业对于自身和员工的期待和要求。当然，这也是最表层的方式。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;最有效的方式，是通过实习或工作，去验证企业的价值主张。事实上，没有比在一起工作，更能够了解一个群体的工作方式和态度的了。你完全可以观察身边优秀的同事，看他们是如何工作，如何沟通；而他们的态度是否部分体现了企业的价值主张。一般来说，越是优秀的员工，他们越敬业、越投入，越有召唤力，而且业绩越好。从某种意义上讲，这批人代表着企业精神，关系着企业的可持续发展。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;最后，了解和认同企业的价值观是出发点，但绝不是目的地。最要紧的是将所“知”转化为所“行”。积极融入企业，按照企业所鼓励的方式去工作，才能迈好入职第一步。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161202/1480659725800450.jpg\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1480659725800450.jpg\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;640.webp (2).jpg\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-tools=\\&quot;135编辑器\\&quot; data-id=\\&quot;88184\\&quot; data-color=\\&quot;rgb(94, 145, 189)\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-width=\\&quot;100%\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 670px; vertical-align: top;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12.8px; transform: translate3d(3px, 0px, 0px);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-brushtype=\\&quot;text\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 2em; line-height: 2em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(94, 145, 189);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 简而言之 &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; border-left: 1em solid rgb(94, 145, 189); font-size: 16px; border-top: 1em solid transparent !important; border-bottom: 1em solid transparent !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; border-right: 0.6em solid rgb(94, 145, 189); border-top: 0.6em solid rgb(94, 145, 189); border-left: 0.6em solid transparent !important; border-bottom: 0.6em solid transparent !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-width=\\&quot;100%\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 670px; vertical-align: top; border-width: 0px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-width=\\&quot;100%\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 654px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 2px dashed rgb(160, 160, 160); border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;企业理想的人才是“德才兼备，以德为先”。国际知名人力资源大师戴维·尤里奇提出了一个简单的人才公式：人才（Talent）=素质（competency）×爱岗敬业(commitment)×贡献(contribution)。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;这里对人才的要求则更进一步。对于企业来说不但需要有工作能力，愿意工作，并按企业要求完成任务（价值观），更要通过工作为公司的发展做出切实的贡献。如果一名员工既有能力，也愿意做事，却对公司没有贡献，对于企业来说，这名员工的才华和热情便失去了意义。&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\&quot;&gt;最后的最后，祝愿：每位职场新人都能收获满满，马到功成！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '企业理想的人才是“德才兼备，以德为先”', '职场新人，你知道企业需要什么样的人才吗？', '/Uploads/Picture/uploads/20161202/584114225a370.jpg', '0', '2016-12-02', null, null, '0', null, null, '0', '', '1', '0', '1', null, null, '');
INSERT INTO `uha_classnews` VALUES ('47', '&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;前段时间，咪蒙的一篇《职场不相信眼泪》在网上掀起了“实习生该不该一天帮老板拿5次外卖”的讨论，支持者认为职场新人帮老板干点杂事无可厚非，也有人讨伐称实习生可不是来帮你拿外卖的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;孰是孰非，难以说清，但有一件事是肯定的，在职场，没有那么多给玻璃心生长的土壤，或者说，没有一份工作是不委屈的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161206/1480993657892299.gif\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1480993657892299.gif\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;0 (2).gif\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-author=\\&quot;Wxeditor\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 5px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 2em; height: 2em; border: 1px solid rgb(5, 157, 127); transform: rotate(45deg);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 7px 0px 0px -8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 2em; height: 2em; background-color: rgb(5, 157, 127);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; transform: rotate(-45deg); width: 28px; height: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 19.2px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;01&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(5, 157, 127);\\&quot;&gt; 谁的职场不委屈 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;公司一个90后的男孩子辞了职之后过来跟我辞行。他是公司去年校招的一批培训生之一，身上具备了阳光、聪明、富有激情等优点。在新人中，HR及很多老员工是相当看好他的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;他一提出辞职，听闻的相关人员都极力挽留。但他铁了心地要离开，表情里有着一点毅然决然，甚至带着一些忿恨。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section label=\\&quot;Copyright © 2015 playhudong All Rights Reserved.\\&quot; donone=\\&quot;shifuMouseDownCard(&amp;#39;shifu_c_038&amp;#39;)\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 15px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); width: 670px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;text-decoration: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(5, 157, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;他说，“我实在受不了他的咆哮，他像疯了一般当众骂我，太伤自尊了。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;他口中的“他”是他的直属领导，一个对自己和別人都要求甚高的人，性格里有那么点急躁。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=\\&quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161206/1480992907147382.gif\\&quot; title=\\&q