t; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote class=\\&quot;\\&quot; data-author=\\&quot;Wxeditor\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 5px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section style=\\&quot;margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 2em; height: 2em; border: 1px solid rgb(5, 157, 127); transform: rotate(45deg);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;section class=\\&quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;margin: 7px 0px 0px -8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 2em; height: 2em; background-color: rgb(5, 157, 127);\\&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; transform: rotate(-45deg); width: 28px; height: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 19.2px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;03&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(5, 157, 127);\\&quot;&gt; 将委屈转化为成长，转化成进步的养料 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;职场的委屈也不是站得越高就会像空气一样稀薄。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;color: rgb(5, 157, 127); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;真正站得高走得远的人，反而都是比一般人更能消化委屈，也是比一般人吃了更多委屈的人。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;color: rgb(5, 157, 127); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;只不过，在委屈面前，他们能更好地消化，将委屈转化为成长，转化成进步的养料。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;听闻，集团某领导甚能骂人，其流传在各个分公司的骂人事件层出不穷。其骂人有一个特点就是目标专一，也就是说在某一时间段，该领导批评大骂的对象唯一，穷追不舍。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;话说，在有次集团高层月度会议上，此领导在此次会议上展现了他不同寻常的骂人功底。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\\&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161206/1480993795984594.gif\\&quot; title=\\&quot;1480993795984594.gif\\&quot; alt=\\&quot;0 (3).gif\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;会议第一天，在销售部通报月度销售数据时，此领导一听数据，一抬头，对着正好坐在自己对面的某分总大骂，指责其业绩表现极差，足足骂了近一个小时。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;此间，该分总脸涨得通红，一言未发，却暗自思忖，自己业绩也不是全国倒数后三名，何以独独被破口大骂呢？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;茶歇时，其他参会人员纷纷调侃某分总，挨骂的分总也自嘲，认为一定是座位选得不好，正好坐在了领导对面。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;会议第二天，挨骂的分总学聪明了，选了一个某领导背后的位置，心想领导背后的位置比较安全，起码抬头看不见。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;却不成想，在财务通报财务指标时，该分总所在的分公司盈利情况欠佳。某领导抬头欲破口大骂，却发现找不到某分总了，扭头发现其“躲”在自己身后，顿时更加火冒三丈，各种臭骂，难听无比。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;厉害之处在于，某领导当天的各种“骂”与第一天居然毫不重复。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;会议第三天，按照议程安排，当日无数据通报，主要是议题讨论之类的内容。连着挨了两天骂的某分总终于松了一口气，但是依然不敢掉以轻心，相当谨慎地找了一个靠近柱子的位置。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;这个位置从某领导的角度来看，不那么轻易被看得到。哪成想，在某领导做会议总结时，又提到某分总，左右张望未寻到人影，气得摔了手边的笔：业绩做那么差，开个会还躲来躲去，给我滚出来！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;某分总颤巍巍地挪了出来。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;又是一场惊天动地、“总结式”的大骂。最后实在无话可骂的时候，某分总连发型和普通话的发音都被该领导多角度多维度地痛骂、鄙视了一番。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;在全国同仁面前，被领导全方位、无死角地痛骂，是不是更有理由“玻璃心”？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;但是，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(5, 157, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;某分总没有时间“玻璃心”，立刻投入了接下来的战斗中。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(5, 157, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;次月，各项指标略有改善，某分总在月度会议中逃过“痛骂”，云淡风轻地看领导换了一个臭骂对象。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=\\&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=\\&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/